<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge">&#x1F3C6; For Cyclists Who've Lost KOMs</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Every KOM Deserves<br />
      <em>a Proper Funeral.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Log your King of the Mountain achievements. When someone steals your crown,
      give it the send-off it deserves — complete with a funny obituary and a
      shareable memorial image.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Create Free Account</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Sign In</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">How it Works</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F6B4;</div>
        <h3>Log Your KOMs</h3>
        <p>Add any segment you currently hold. Enter the name, the date you got it, and optional Strava link or notes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1FAA6;</div>
        <h3>Memorialize the Fallen</h3>
        <p>When you lose a KOM, hit the memorial button. Record the date, who beat you, and get a hilariously generated obituary.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F5BC;</div>
        <h3>Shareable PNG Image</h3>
        <p>Download a ready-to-post 1080×1080 memorial card with all the details — perfect for Instagram or your cycling group chat.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F4CA;</div>
        <h3>Your Full KOM History</h3>
        <p>See every KOM you've ever held — active crowns and memorialized ones — with a count of exactly how many days you ruled.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>Ready to immortalise your suffering?</h2>
    <p>Free to use. No Strava API. No tracking. Just beautiful obituaries.</p>
    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Started — It's Free</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
